      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It is very important that you do not change your warfarin dosage without consulting your healthcare provider first. Your current dose is based on blood tests to ensure your blood is at the correct clotting level for your heart condition. Any changes, even small ones, must be managed by your doctor who can monitor your INR levels closely to maintain safety. Please schedule an appointment to discuss your symptoms and review your medication plan.",
